<h2 id="classes">Classes</h2>
<p>
  A character class is a fundamental part of the identity and nature of characters in the Dungeons &
  Dragons role-playing game. A character's capabilities, strengths, and weaknesses are largely
  defined by its class. A character's class affects a character's available skills and abilities.
</p>

